<span class="text-xs font-semibold px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/20 text-yellow-700 dark:bg-yellow-400/30 dark:text-yellow-300">Revisión Final</span>
</div>
<p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">Juan Pérez - Toyota Camry 2021</p>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Actualizado: 22 de Julio, 2024</p>
</div>
