<p class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white font-bold">Orden #84319</p>
<span class="text-xs font-semibold px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-500/20 text-green-700 dark:bg-green-400/30 dark:text-green-300">Trabajo Terminado</span>
</div>
